00:18:58.190 --> 00:19:00.760
<i>Dobrodošli u apartman "Beč."</i>

00:19:02.030 --> 00:19:03.520
O, da.

00:19:08.350 --> 00:19:09.790
Što?

00:19:17.190 --> 00:19:19.350
<i>O, da! O, da!</i> 
-Da!

00:19:19.430 --> 00:19:20.950
Daj mi duplu porciju velikih račića.

