Hectore, molim te. Još jednu.

00:19:51.630 --> 00:19:52.630
<i>Da, gospodine.</i>

00:19:53.230 --> 00:19:54.230
Hvala.

00:19:56.670 --> 00:19:59.240
<i>O, da! O, da! O, da!</i>

00:20:06.630 --> 00:20:08.430
Gubite se odavde!

